name: Propertyfinder
tagline: A objective c helper class to find properties in a class definition
body:
# PropertyFinder
A objective c helper class to find properties in a class definition.
This lib's implementation is inspired by JSONModel (<https://github.com/icanzilb/JSONModel>)


## Release Notes:
**Version 0.0.1**:

*   Create the Property Finder class.
*   Add a method to find a property name which annotated by a arbitrary protocol
*   Add an example project
